Yield-Per-Recruit

ypr.Rd

Yield-Per-Recruit

ypr(tmax = 20L, k = 0.5, Linf = 1000, t0 = 0, a = 1e-05, b = 3)

Arguments

tmax

The maximum age.
k

The growth coefficient.
Linf

The mean maximum length.
t0

The age at length 0.
a

The condition factor.
b

The scaling exponent.
